   "source": [
    "# Prompt Caching"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "0470bd1d",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Helps to speed up and reduce cost of Claude responses"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "abeee367",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "By default, Claude does not store all the prompt and response data."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "ceb79155",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Can create a temporary data store for Claude to persist some of it's previous work. This is **prompt caching**"
   ]
  }
